<h2 id="intro">Introduction</h2>
<p><strong>MITE:BE</strong> (Minecraft Is Too Easy: Break Everything) is an extremely hardcore survival mod for Minecraft 1.6.4. Unlike vanilla Minecraft, you can't just punch a tree and rush to diamonds — instead, you must progress step by step through a completely redesigned crafting and material system, starting from gathering grass with your bare hands all the way to defeating the Ender Dragon with adamantium gear.</p>

