<h2 id="new-mechanics">New Mechanics</h2>
<p>MITE:BE introduces many new systems on top of vanilla Minecraft:</p>

<h3 id="game-modes">🎮 Game Modes — Simple vs Hardcore</h3>
<p>MITE:BE has two fundamental game modes. <strong>Simple (Survivor)</strong> mode is for learning and exploration, while <strong>Hardcore</strong> is the ultimate, brutal challenge. There are <em>many</em> mechanical differences between them!</p>

<div class="warning-box">⚠️ <strong>This wiki applies to BOTH modes by default.</strong> Where mode-specific differences exist, they are explicitly marked. If not indicated, the mechanic works the same in both modes.</div>

<table class="compare-table">
