</table>
<div class="tip-card">🌡️ <strong>Modifiers (warming):</strong> Lava (within 2 blocks): +0.1°C/35s · Fire (within 3 blocks): +0.1°C/50s · Holding a torch: +0.1°C/60s · On fire (burning): +0.1°C/5s · Nether: constant +0.4°C · Sprinting: +0.1°C/90s (capped at 37°C) · Desert daytime: +0.1°C/hour<br>🌡️ <strong>Modifiers (cooling):</strong> Submerging in water: −0.1°C/5s · Holding ice: −0.1°C/25s · Eating ice cream: −0.1°C · Sleeping on ground: −0.2–0.4°C (random)</div>

<h4 id="curses">Curses &amp; Ailments</h4>
<p>Witches can inflict 16 different curses. You must kill that specific witch to remove it, or use a dispel potion. Only one curse is active at a time:</p>
