</table>
<h4>Diabetes</h4>
<p>Eating fruits, sugar, and sweets fills an insulin resistance meter (+4,800 per sweet food). It decays naturally (1,200/minute). Milk does <strong>not</strong> cure it!</p>
<table class="compare-table">
  <tr><th>Threshold</th><th>Level</th><th>Duration</th><th>Effect</th></tr>
