  <tr style="background:rgba(255,200,0,0.08)">
    <td><strong>Acidity</strong></td>
    <td>1 pt/30s during fog</td>
    <td>10: Weakness I · 20: +Slowness I (damage every 40s) · 30: +Hunger I + Blindness I (damage every 20s)</td>
  </tr>
  <tr style="background:rgba(100,150,255,0.10)">
    <td><strong>Oxygen Deficiency</strong></td>
    <td>1 pt/30s during fog</td>
    <td>10: Weakness I · 20: 0.5 hearts/40s + Slowness I · 30: 0.5 hearts/30s + Blindness I</td>
  </tr>
  <tr style="background:rgba(100,255,100,0.08)">
    <td><strong>High Oxygen</strong> (Jungle &lt;Y50)</td>
    <td>Active during fog</td>
    <td>5 min: Haste I · 10 min: +Speed I · 20 min: +HP Regen · 40 min: Weakness I + Hunger I + Mining Fatigue I (overexposure!)</td>
  </tr>
</table>
<div class="info-box">💊 <strong>Cures:</strong> Acidity: submerge in water (−2/10s) or Skin Care Bottle (double protection for 10 min). Oxygen Deficiency: move above Y45 (+1/2s recovery) or Oxygen Bottle (−4 pts each).</div>

<h4 id="moon-cycle">Moon Cycle</h4>
<p>The moon has 7 different phases — each with unique effects! The most severe is the <strong>Blood Moon</strong>, which evolves 6 times, spawning increasingly powerful zombies.</p>
