  <tr style="background:rgba(255,255,100,0.10)"><td><strong>🟡 Yellow Moon</strong></td><td>Day 32n−8 (days 24, 56, 120…)</td><td>Crop growth +200% · harvest yield +1 per ripe crop</td></tr>
