<div class="tip-card">🌱 <strong>Manure:</strong> Applied to farmland, it increases crop yields. <strong>Warning:</strong> If you haven't defecated in 3+ days (and meter is 50+) and/or plant nutrition is below 20%, the duration doubles. If both conditions apply: up to 5 minutes!</div>

<h4 id="world-marker">World Marker</h4>
<p>The <strong>World Marker</strong> (Respawn Anchor) is a special block that functions as an <strong>automatic respawn point</strong>. If you die near one, you respawn there.</p>
<ul>
  <li>A countdown starts after placing it — the respawn point is temporarily active</li>
  <li>Also useful as a navigation marker and base indicator in the Underground</li>
</ul>
<div class="warning-box">⚠️ <strong>Does not work in Hardcore mode</strong> — the World Marker only provides a respawn point in Simple mode.</div>
<div class="info-box">📜 <strong>Knowledge Book:</strong> Can be found in Pillager Fortress loot chests. Unlocks new recipes — then transforms into a <em>Book item</em> that grants XP. <abbr class="src-cl" title="Source: mod changelog (mcmod.cn) — not personally verified">📜 changelog</abbr></div>

