  <tr><td>2</td><td>Enter Underground dimension</td><td>Portal on bedrock → obtain Ancient Metal</td></tr>
  <tr><td>3</td><td>Ancient Metal Workbench</td><td>Unlocks advanced electronics recipes</td></tr>
  <tr><td>4</td><td><strong>Obsidian Furnace Core</strong></td><td>8× Obsidian + Gold/Iron Workbench → heat 3</td></tr>
  <tr><td>5</td><td><strong>Smelt Mithril</strong></td><td>⚠️ Lava Bucket required (heat 3)! Iron Pickaxe mines it!</td></tr>
  <tr><td>6</td><td><strong>Mithril Pickaxe</strong></td><td>Mine Obsidian ore → Nether portal material (harvest level 4)</td></tr>
  <tr><td>7</td><td><strong>Prepare for Nether</strong> (see checklist below!)</td><td>Mithril armor + weapon recommended (minimum Iron)</td></tr>
  <tr><td>8</td><td>Nether → <strong>obtain Blaze Rods</strong></td><td>⚠️ Blaze Rods required for Adamantium smelting (heat 4)!</td></tr>
