  <tr><td>10</td><td><strong>Smelt Adamantium</strong></td><td>⚠️ Blaze Rod (heat 4) + Netherrack Furnace required! Mithril Pickaxe mines it!</td></tr>
  <tr><td>11</td><td>Defeat the Wither Boss</td><td>Nether Star → needed to build the Bedrock Pulverizer</td></tr>
  <tr><td>12</td><td><strong>Bedrock Pulverizer</strong></td><td>The key to opening the End portal</td></tr>
  <tr><td>13</td><td><strong>Defeat the Ender Dragon</strong></td><td>Full adamantium armor + weapon strongly recommended</td></tr>
</table>

<div class="info-box"><strong>🔥 Nether Entry Prerequisites — Don't go in without these!</strong>
<ul style="margin:4px 0 0 0">
  <li>✅ <strong>Mithril armor and weapon recommended</strong> (minimum Iron, but you can already smelt Mithril!)</li>
  <li>✅ <strong>Mithril Sword</strong> or better weapon (Iron minimum)</li>
  <li>✅ At least 2 food portions + filled water flask</li>
  <li>✅ <strong>Something Gold</strong> — Zombie Pigmen are immediately aggressive without it</li>
  <li>✅ Spare armor pieces — the Nether is lethal!</li>
  <li>✅ At least 30 torches</li>
</ul></div>

<div class="warning-box">⚠️ <strong>Most common end-game mistakes:</strong>
<ul style="margin:4px 0 0 0">
  <li>Trying to smelt Mithril with coal/wood → heat 2 is not enough, <strong>Lava Bucket required!</strong></li>
  <li>Trying to smelt Adamantium with lava → heat 3 not enough, <strong>Blaze Rod (heat 4) + Netherrack Furnace required!</strong></li>
  <li>Going for Adamantium ore without a Mithril Pickaxe → cannot be mined!</li>
  <li>Entering the Nether without iron armor → near-certain death</li>
  <li>Not collecting enough Nether Skulls before attempting the Wither Boss</li>
</ul></div>

