<h2 id="skills">Skills & Professions</h2>

<div class="warning-box">
  <strong>⚙️ Professions must be enabled!</strong><br>
  They are disabled by default. To enable:<br>
  <ul style="margin:6px 0 0 0">
    <li><strong>In-game command:</strong> <code>/skills on</code> — requires cheats to be enabled</li>
    <li><strong>NBT editing:</strong> add <code>are_skills_enabled = true</code> (byte tag) to <code>level.dat</code></li>
    <li><strong>Check status:</strong> <code>/skills</code> — lists all professions if enabled</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<h3>The Level & XP System</h3>
<p>In MITE:BE, your <strong>level</strong> directly affects gameplay. Levels range from <strong>-40 to +200</strong> — death drains XP, so your level can drop!</p>

