</table>

<h3>Heat Management</h3>
<p>The furnace displays its current temperature. Different ores have different melting points. Temperature drops over time.</p>

<div class="tip"><strong>Infinite heating:</strong> Place an infinite lava source at the bottom of the multiblock furnace for infinite heat! Multiple lava sources stack!</div>

<h3>Lava Bucket Melt Chance</h3>
<p>When using lava-heated furnaces, metal items have a <strong>material-dependent chance</strong> of accidentally melting and being lost. Higher-tier metals have better heat resistance.</p>
<table class="compare-table">
  <tr><th>Material</th><th>Melt Chance</th></tr>
  <tr style="background:rgba(255,100,50,0.15)"><td><span class="tier t-copper">Copper / Silver</span></td><td>16%</td></tr>
  <tr style="background:rgba(255,150,30,0.20)"><td><span class="tier t-silver">Gold</span></td><td>20% ⚠️</td></tr>
  <tr><td><span class="tier t-iron">Iron</span></td><td>8%</td></tr>
  <tr><td><span class="tier t-hard">Hardstone</span></td><td>4%</td></tr>
  <tr><td><span class="tier t-ancient">Ancient Metal</span></td><td>2%</td></tr>
  <tr><td><span class="tier t-mithril">Mithril</span></td><td>1%</td></tr>
  <tr style="background:rgba(100,200,100,0.12)"><td><span class="tier t-adamantium">Adamantium</span></td><td>0% ✅</td></tr>
</table>
<div class="tip-card">🔥 <strong>Gold warning:</strong> Gold items have the highest melt chance (20%)! Be careful with gold items near lava-heated furnaces.</div>


<!-- ===== IRON ===== -->

<h2 id="iron">Iron & Steel</h2>
<p>Iron is obtained from the multiblock furnace. After the iron age comes high carbon steel.</p>

<h3>Iron Pickaxe — Critical Milestone!</h3>
<p>Iron pickaxe can mine <strong>mithril ore</strong>! This is your first real entry into the mythic age.</p>

<h3>High Carbon Steel</h3>
<p>Iron + Carbon Crystal = High Carbon Steel. The final alloy. Strong enough to cut through the darkness of the Underground.</p>
<div class="info">The high carbon steel pickaxe has <strong>chain mining</strong>: hold the button to break multiple blocks at once!</div>
<div class="tip-card">⚒️ <strong>Alloying in the furnace:</strong> Place the <strong>iron tool</strong> (sword, pickaxe, etc.) in the slot ABOVE the fuel slot, and the <strong>Carbon Crystal</strong> in the left-side slot. This converts it to steel.</div>


