<h3>Food Nutrition Values</h3>
<p>MITE:BE tracks 4 nutrients: <strong>Satiation</strong> (hunger fill), <strong>Nutrition</strong> (actual nourishment), <strong>Protein</strong>, and <strong>Phytonutrients</strong>. <strong>IR</strong> (Insulin Response) appears on sugary foods — an overly sweet diet degrades energy levels!</p>
