<h3>Advanced Foods</h3>
<p>Beef stew, chicken soup, vegetable cream soup, pumpkin soup, ice cream, cheese, porridge, cereal, chocolate... the Cook profession unlocks complex recipes.</p>

<h3>Farming</h3>
