<h3>Enchantability by Material</h3>
<p>Higher enchantability = better and more enchantment options. Non-enchantable materials: Obsidian, Netherrack, Glass, Rusted Iron.</p>
<div id="material-enchantability"></div>
<div class="info-box">💡 <strong>Tip:</strong> Mithril weapons offer the same excellent enchanting odds as Diamond (both 100), while also achieving Masterwork+ quality. Gold (50) is also good for enchanting, but its low durability makes it less practical.</div>

