<!-- ===== KNOWLEDGE BOOKS ===== -->

<div class="collapsible"><div class="collapsible-toggle" role="button" tabindex="0" aria-expanded="false"><h3>Knowledge Books</h3><span class="toggle-icon">▶</span></div><div class="collapsible-body"><div class="collapsible-body-inner">
<p>The Knowledge Book is a special item used to unlock advanced crafting recipes. Until you have the required knowledge book, the recipe won't appear in the built-in recipe book or on the workbench.</p>

<h3>How to obtain?</h3>
<p>Knowledge books are found in <strong>chests</strong> with a random drop chance. Not only in Underworld dungeon chests, but also in overworld generated structures — such as <strong>Pillager Outposts</strong> (which can be substantial settlements with tall towers and proper buildings).</p>

<h3>How to use?</h3>
<div class="flow">
  <span class="flow-item">Chest (Dungeon / Structure)</span>
  <span class="flow-arrow">→</span>
  <span class="flow-item">Knowledge Book</span>
  <span class="flow-arrow">→</span>
  <span class="flow-item">Right-click (consumed)</span>
  <span class="flow-arrow">→</span>
  <span class="flow-item">Recipe Unlocked!</span>
