<h2 id="ancient-metal">Ancient Metal</h2>
<p>An evil and terrifying ancient power resides within. Ancient Metal is the most mysterious material from the Underground.</p>

<h3>Set Bonus (4/4 pieces)</h3>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Reinforcement I:</strong> -30% Damage from the Underground</li>
  <li><strong>Reinforcement II:</strong> Underground Vampire Bats won't attack you</li>
  <li>Worn armor is resilient to corrosion</li>
  <li>Can hit Phase Spiders (sword)</li>
</ul>

<h3>Reinforcement</h3>
